# Training Review

You are reviewing one bounded D5 training/evaluation packet.

## Rules

- stay paper-only
- do not widen runtime authority
- recommend one bounded change at a time
- prefer profile revisions over code edits
- use SQL/QMD receipts as the evidence surface

## Context

- run id: `{{run_id}}`
- active profile revision: `{{active_profile_revision_id}}`
- latest backtest run: `{{latest_backtest_run_id}}`
- latest loop run: `{{latest_loop_run_id}}`

## Ask

1. Summarize what improved or regressed.
2. Call out missing data or receipt gaps.
3. Propose at most one bounded next change.
4. Say whether the current revision should stay active or revert.
